Sales Electrical Engineer Job (Electrical Manufacturing) Jakarta, Indonesia  -
Sales Electrical Engineer Job (Electrical Manufacturing) Jakarta, Indonesia
Responsibilities
Monroe Consulting Group is recruiting for a Multinational company that has been active in the Electrical Manufacturing Sector. Our client is seeking a professional, with a background in electrical engineering, to fill the job of Electrical Engineer, to be based in Jakarta, Indonesia. Our client has become a worldwide leader in their industry segment and delivers value to its clients by betting on constant business development, advertising excellence and high-quality human resources. The winning candidate will experience a dynamic, stimulating and international environment, allowing them to grow professionally. The company offers good prospects for career progression Key job responsibilities will include: To help in analysis and interpretation of bid documentsBe in charge of electrical project managementBe in charge of cost estimations in proposals, technical offers and specificationsMaintain relationship with customers and suppliersPerforming sales activity assigned to ensure in achieving an optimum level of business.Responsible for formulating and implementing short terms and mid terms Sales Strategy. Accountable for the achievements of Sales volume targets and growth within specific assignmentResponsible for the evaluations and approval of sales proposal prior to proposal release.  Evaluations must cover legal and commercial aspectResponsible for establishing customer or prospect interface and retaining valuable clients for future businessResponsible for all required reporting to be available in timely mannerIncumbent should develop Sales Strategy with Sales ManagerEnsure that Commercial, legal and technical aspects are being done properly to minimized company risk and maximized profit. Job Requirements  Bachelor in Electrical Engineering Degree2 – 3 years experiences in electrical projectsStrong networking in government/private companiesCost EstimationExcellent team work and organizational skillsExcellent English communication skills, both written and verbal. All applications will be treated in the strictest of confidence. If you are a suitable match for this position please send your application to Industrial@monroeconsulting.com
